      <ul class="credential-highlights">
        <li><span>Bonded &amp; insured</span><span>Errors &amp; Omissions policy: $100,000</span></li>
        <li><span>Background checks</span><span>Sterling Verified, renewed annually</span></li>
        <li><span>Professional memberships</span><span>National Notary Association · American Society of Notaries</span></li>
      </ul>

      <div class="credential-actions" data-animate="cta">
        <a href="#contact" class="credential-cta">Request credential packet</a>
        <a href="tel:+12673099000" class="credential-cta credential-cta--outline">Talk with our notary</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
